I have been in a raving good mood lately. There is so much to think about right now, and so many exciting things going on First, I finally went and purchased some well thought about, well needed studio lights Second, since I purchsed them, I have been trying to book jobs to pay them off, and have been pleasingly succesful with it. Third, my birthday is in less then 2 weeks, and christmas is a week after that!! How can iInot be in a good mood, and to top it off, I get to go to a PUG PARTY tommorow at Hot Diggity Dog. I dont really know exactly what a pug party is, but i assume lots of pugs will be there, therefore making me a really happy girl Also at Hot Diggity Dog next Saturday, this will be happening.... And who doesn't love dogs & funny photos!! This month is going to be sooo busy, but I am looking forward to all of it!

this morgan with our friend max's baby, cloud So this is officially ( as of next week) going to be the new house that Robin and I are going to live in!! We move middle of next week!1 I cant wait, its this tiny little heritage home that was built in 1860!! Its soo adorable, I am beyond excited!! Miss Jennifer Kennedy Miss Stefanie Hunt/Huuzanga(i think i spelt it right), and Miss Jessica Hunt I took all these photos with my new/used twin lens rolleiflex, i love love my new camera, by far my best purchase this year. I havent really used my digi since i bought this camera Its taking me back to my roots, i love it

me and aki at my bachlorette party at the only cafe me at the same place, 9all of these are taken by aki) me draggin robin home after his bachelor party (which we crashed) robin and I at our wedding dinner
i just had the most wonderful day, i was in love with all of it

is it weird that i am actually lookin forward to winter this year so that i can relax for 2 seconds

my summer has been insanely busy, i'm working 2 jobs again plus shooting weddings every weekend

For example, here is my schedul for the next week
Today- wedding
saturday-work 9-2, (then i get to go campin for one night!!)
sunday- work 4-10
monday- work 7:30 am -3
tuesday- work 7:30 am-3
wednesday- work job #1 12-4, job #2 6-10
thursday -  off!! probably spend the day editing weddings
friday- work 11:30-8

ya, so i am looking forward to camping with robin though
we got a sweet tent for a wedding present, so we need to use it
other then that
friends are good, my husband is more then awesome, i love my life, i just need 
a bit more downtime, i feel like a lame-o if i stay inside all day when its so
nice outside, does anyone hear me?

i finally got all the photos back from morgan!! here a few to start off, just rehersal party pics from the day before the wedding!! and p.s. if its possible i love my husband more then i did yesterday!!
breakfast diner in montreal leaving the train station from coburg more under here

i am now officially a married woman and loving it
we jsut got back from montreal had a wicked time,
now we are leaving to go camping in a sweet rental car!!
see you all when we get back
i broke my toe and my foot is turning blue

i went to a danny michel concert last night that was pretty awesome, but the more awesome part is that i went to hang out downstairs at the only beforehand, and danny michel and his band came out on the patio looking for a seat and i offered them to share our table, so we got to hang out with them, and take some photos, it was sweet this is christine this is her again danny michel eating a sandwich danny michel and his drummer and his keyboarder, whos name is terrance, he hung out with leonard cohen last week and had sweet stories about it his drummer

there are only 16 more days till my wedding!!! but i am still being the least stressed out bride i have ever met i think i am so calm that its starting to annoy some people but things are going well, dress fitting and making favours tonight aki is going to be here soon!! the food is taken care of, the yard at my grandmas house (where the ceremony is) is looking beautiful, i have a ton of flowers overtaking my apartment window that are going to soon be bouquets for me and my girls, the flower girl dresses are being made on friday, by me, jenny and my mom. things are all coming together and i cant wait.

i noticed that its been a while since i have updated my live journal with writing.
jenn actually pointed it out yesterday, she wanted me to update it with stuff about her!!!
stef also i think would like to me just update my lj with things about her, i think its the only reason either of you check it
NERDS
anyways last saturday jenn and stef and linz threw a super fun personal shower for me, and i was indeed showered with lots and lots of sexy outfits!! it was really fun, they made sexy food, and a sexy guest book, and made me wear a corset all night long, and made me try on all the items i was given!
this week amongst my crazy work schedule, we got the apt done being painted, and we got new shelves, dressers, and closet bars, thanks to my dad, who is super man
ive got to hang out with my new little brother alot too, i love him tooo much
this week hes discovered his manhood, and its been quite amusing! we've had to teach him why its private and that he cant pull it out in public. he now likes to inform people of that -his sentence of the week- "sorry i am not allowed to show you my willy" !!! kids are sooo funny
other then that, less then 7 weeks till the wedding!! i am starting to feel like i have 2 million things to do, but i dont know exactly what they are! 
anyways, 2 more shifts then i have some time off, which i need to get some things done!!
so out for now
blogged

Its official,this beautiful little boy is now my little brother Some crazy stuff went on last week, consisting of his mother giving him up and signing him over to my mom so as of yesterday, I officially have a 3 year old brother!! I love him like crazy! Connor

i'm going to go ahead and pull a pierre and not put a cut for all these photos i am about to post what a WONDERFUL WEEKEND i am absolutly exhausted, but it was well worth it We began moving in to our new apt Saturday early morning, we had family over all day cleaning and moving we got mostly everything in!! Then we had an official house warming party on Saturday night, it was great we had lots of people over and drank and ate in our new place, it was soo awesome. Then today we did adult stuff, like went to home depot and bought a hammer and a broom and spent the day rearranging , cleaning, and playing indoor soccer in the apt!! its so nice to finally have our own place heres some pics this was before we started moving in in the morning this was the men trying to put the couches together, took 5 of them an hour to do it!! us sitting on our newly put together couch robin smelling my hair!! other anlge of the apt robin posing it up for me, looking pretty hot in his rolled up pinstripe pants final result of our hard work today!

so we took these, the first one we took of ourselves, and the second one a friend took we want to put one pic on half the wedding invites, and the othe pic on the other half, just to mix it up a bit what does everyone think? is the 2nd one too cheezy?? i think i like it, i think with the rebate edges and the texturing on it, i hope it made it a little less cheezy, i am a girl, and i cant help liking a little cheeziness here and there!!

here is the photo of the large truck that hit our car, after it hit us then continued to drive the wrong way up a one way street, onto the sidewalk and into a sign!! way to go!! this is a photo of the back of the truck and the cop cars and these are lovely photos of our smashed car, after a drunk drive drove into us while were stoppped, after we stopped because he almost head on hit the guy infront of us, driving up a one way street, then continued to pull around that guy, and drive into our car, then into a sign!! gotta love stupid people also gotta love spending the whole night at the police station, and probably not getting enough $$$ to fix or buy a new car!! friggin no fault insurance!!

and its gorgeous, i will post a pic soon
i took off all my other rings and now its the only one on my hand
its so pretty, i didnt think i was diamond ring kinda girl, but its so sparkly!!
i feel like such a girly girl, but i love it
i cant belive i am getting MARRIED in 5 months, it hasnt sunk it,  its so crazy
but im soo happy, and i dont have any fears as of yet!!!
